snippet.textDisplay:
@joshua cheung where do you think the water part of black water come from? Check your WC the water in the pan and flush cistern both come from the same pipe, the drinking water tap. 

All you have to do is poop in a bag. Heat up that bag to poop to remove the water, odor and pathogens. All remains are a few hundred grams of solid waste. 

Why all that plumbing,  discarded portable water for a few hundred grams of solid waste per poop?

